source.name: Green Vehicle Guide Data Extraction Tool
source.description: The U.S. Environmental Protection Agency's Green Vehicle Guide provides vehicle ratings based on emissions and fuel economy. This data extraction tool allows download by user-selected model year (2000 - current) and format.
